- Who ever said anything about easy? -
Good Wednesday everyone! So I wanted to set the day in right with a kick ass functional training session 💪😜 so I was at the gym when the doors opened, stepping into an empty gym does have a vibe 😎 but I quickly tackled my monster training session which was a triple threat mix of 3 men's health UK workouts! The 1000cal burn, the Battle Game and the Kettle Mettle 💪😤 basically a combo of battleropes, kettlebells, box jumps, plyos and medicine ball circuits that will leave you heaving afterwards 💪😅 loved every minute of it and I'm surely going to be sore tomorrow ^^ after a good stretch and shower I headed home for my breakfast: my new favorite OvenBaked Oatmeal with apple raisin cinnamon and Golden Syrup Whey 👌😋💕 topped with banana 🍌 ZeroSyrup! And a shaker of creatine! Now that I'm topped off I can hit my study books to prepare for my upcoming exam 📚😊 best way for me to work: Train, eat, study, sleep. Repeat grind. Cheers everyone ☕😄

Not going to lie, I'm not 💯% comfortable in my own skin right now. Im not as lean as I'd like to be and my clothes are fitting just a taaaad tight 😆 I've also been 💯% off track the last few weeks bc, life. Time to get back 🙌🏼. If you've hit a slump, lost motivation or simply felt like you needed some time off and are now feeling like you've lost all progress, you haven't.
